The splash timing can be modified by changing the coresponding numbers from 150-900
in the line below located inside the
"Steam-Saturn-Pre-Load/contents/splash/Splash.qml" file

source: "images/animation_to_gif_MOTION_x_900.gif"

Valid images would be:
animation_to_gif_MOTION_x_150.gif
animation_to_gif_MOTION_x_200.gif
animation_to_gif_MOTION_x_250.gif
animation_to_gif_MOTION_x_300.gif
animation_to_gif_MOTION_x_350.gif
animation_to_gif_MOTION_x_400.gif
animation_to_gif_MOTION_x_450.gif
animation_to_gif_MOTION_x_500.gif
animation_to_gif_MOTION_x_550.gif
animation_to_gif_MOTION_x_600.gif
animation_to_gif_MOTION_x_650.gif
animation_to_gif_MOTION_x_700.gif
animation_to_gif_MOTION_x_750.gif
animation_to_gif_MOTION_x_800.gif
animation_to_gif_MOTION_x_850.gif
animation_to_gif_MOTION_x_900.gif

Save the file and exit.
